Michael Weatherly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Weatherly 0 Michael Manning Weatherly, Jr., (born July 8, 1968) is an American actor, producer and director who became known for playing the role of Anthony DiNozzo on CBS television series, NCIS (2003–2016). In October 2016, he assumed the role of Jason Bull in Bull. Weatherly is also recognized for his portrayal of Logan Cale in Dark Angel (2000–2002).
